milestones.description: Kwame Tucker and Gibbons's 16-run partnership is BMUDA's highest for the 1st wicket in ODIs, breaking the record of 2 between Kwame Tucker and Daniel Morgan
Romaine and Gibbons's 65-run partnership is BMUDA's highest for the 3rd wicket in ODIs, breaking the record of 8 between Kwame Tucker and Azeem Pitcher
Tucker and Romaine's 34-run partnership is BMUDA's highest for the 4th wicket in ODIs, breaking the record of 6 between Romaine and Kwame Tucker
Tucker has become the top wicket-taker for BMUDA in ODIs with 4 wickets, going past Hasan Durham's 2
Romaine has become the top scorer for BMUDA in ODIs with 87 runs, going past Dean Minors's 46
Hasan Durham has broken the record for playing the most ODIs (2) for BMUDA, going past Lionel Cann
Romaine's 62 is the highest individual score in ODIs (for BMUDA), surpassing Dean Minors's 46
Ryan Steede has conceded the most runs in an innings (68) in ODIs for BMUDA, going past O'Brien's record of 41
Romaine and Gibbons's 65-run partnership is BMUDA's highest for any wicket in ODIs, breaking the record of 64 between Dean Minors and Lionel Cann
